name: Force Push
Lore: 'A fully-trained Sith warrior has more weapons at his disposal than just a lightsaber.',
Text: 'Target opponent''s Jedi with at least one combat card present with your Dark Jedi. Reveal one of target''s combat cards (random selection). If revealed card''s destiny > 4, place it on top of opponent''s Reserve Deck. Otherwise, lose 1 Force. (Immune to Sense.)',
